race.comment: EASY LOVE (10) has hit the top-five in all seven starts to date and doesn't know how to put in a poor one. This is not an overly strong affair and can get a well-deserved victory. LIVALITTLE (5) is one from one around this circuit and gets the reliable Gollan/Jones combination. Bold showing expected. PIERONIMO (7) strips fitter second-up from the break and must be respected out of the astute Archibald barn. Top-three conveyance. BROOKLYN DAISY (8) has placed five of six this campaign and looks to be building up to another win. Don't discount lightly. ARTSPACE (1) makes some appeal with the 3kg claim.
